00:10:42.098 --> 00:10:44.053
Traffic will be functionally exuberant.
交通会在功能上更活跃，

211
00:10:44.077 --> 00:10:46.518
It will be liquid like our blood.
变成血液一样的液体。

212
00:10:46.542 --> 00:10:48.298
